  <trk>
    <name>MUC-L3 — Dolomites North Weekend Loop — Day 2</name>
    <desc>Deploy from MUC and ride into the Dolomites North. Hit Mittenwald and Brenner Pass Approach — 1370m. Loop back to MUC over a packed 2–3 day weekend escape. No highways, just curves and elevation.</desc>
